{"tid":664503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼質疑查鼎或成政治審訊","createTime":"2018-05-14T06:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:06:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75f4ff5ad738d6c92f92cb8c37e57507fe846b66","tid":664503,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390220&d=H1LxElxrqP%2BjdOOa2Pcn9TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5a03e459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390220&h=2de30e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390220</a><br />\n<br />\n李慧琼質疑查鼎或成政治審訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180514/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180514%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=25c35e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周浩鼎及李慧琼昨為東區區會補選候選人植潔鈴拉票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會就譴責民建聯周浩鼎成立的調查委員會早前兩度去信周浩鼎，要求提交資料，但至今未獲回覆，委員會主席石禮謙其後稱會再度去信周要求他配合調查。周浩鼎昨天出席一公開場合時稱不會回應相關事項，民建聯主席李慧琼則引述有意見指，有關調查委員會或會成為「政治審訊」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎拒回應<br />\n<br />\n東區區議會佳曉選區補選候選人之一，民建聯兼工聯會成員植潔鈴昨舉行宣傳活動，李慧琼及周浩鼎亦有出席。周浩鼎以委員會正在進行調查為由，不會回應任何相關事項；李慧琼被問到會否敦促周浩鼎配合調查時邊稱委員會正進行調查，邊指有說法稱調查委員會可能會成為「政治審訊」，故此會了解黨友的取態，並且希望委員會能夠客觀地處理。<br />\n<br />\n立法會2016年就時任特首梁振英收取UGL公司5,000萬元成立專責調查委員會，時任委員會副主席的周浩鼎去年5月涉嫌與梁振英「打龍通」，容許梁修改提交予委員會的文件，周其後辭任委員會副主席，立法會之後成立委員會研究是否需要譴責周浩鼎。而佳曉區補選另有候選人陳真真及李鳳瓊。<br />\n<br />\n■記者許偉賢  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n5男女圖獅子山頭掛港獨標語<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：林鄭好閃得　政治正確排第一 (季陶)"},{"pid":"c7bc832fb5faa2e6ad8deffcf5a51094ab21e85e","tid":664503,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"又無事架啦，奶共做乜都無事。"},{"pid":"cfc1f066388794f4a8e24014f343f6967ddb75fe","tid":664503,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"呢條死八婆點解可以雙重標準到咁既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a6df4ad64ddd9af104e4e7a41a5f866db4a60a","tid":664503,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfc1f066388794f4a8e24014f343f6967ddb75fe","tid":664503,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"呢條死八婆點解可以雙重標準到咁既地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"皆因選民蠢，無偈!<br />\n選民醒你唔會見到佢"},{"pid":"0e8923df8e86eb7137afa5c942db28905cb904cc","tid":664503,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7bc832fb5faa2e6ad8deffcf5a51094ab21e85e","tid":664503,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T06:35:27.000Z","msg":"又無事架啦，奶共做乜都無事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"扮咩吖你五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛未來撚啊廢扮泛民打手<br />\n實質同其他五毛一唱一和<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122237_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F122237_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=778b9c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F122311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b4780c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/122316_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb